    "body": "What does dat look like? For example, I can do the following:\n\nIn [16]: dat = DataFrame(np.random.randn(5, 3))\n\nIn [17]: dat.ix[:, 2] + 2\nOut[17]: \n0    1.681506\n1    1.930261\n2    1.274177\n3    3.159334\n4    3.843346\nName: 2\n\nIn [18]: dat.ix[:, 2] = dat.ix[:, 2] + 2\n\nIn [19]: dat.ix[:, 2]\nOut[19]: \n0    1.681506\n1    1.930261\n2    1.274177\n3    3.159334\n4    3.843346\nName: 2\n"
